name: Time Warp (itch) (kcbramley, SAE Dominic Au)
description:
Time Warp is a procedurally-generated endless runner, wherein which you are tasked in guiding the thanatophobic time wizard, Hauska Kellomies, through a garbled, nonsensical hellscape, in their quest to delay their inevitable death for as long as the logic of the Universe will permit.

This game was developed by SAE Dominic Au, NoahSmith23412 & kcbramley.
